In this strategy, I took advantage of two different sma intersections for buying and selling points. You can use the intersection of 2 sma values for buying and 2 separate sma intersection for selling.

The main purpose of this strategy is to calculate the rate of return of the indicator belonging to this system. You can access the indicator version from this link and set an alarm.
